     /*                                                                     */
     /*  Utility . . . : CRTMSGDS                                           */
     /*  Object  . . . : TESTMSGF                                           */
     /*  Source member : TESTMSGF                                           */
     /*  Source type . : CLLE                                               */
     /*  Description   : Test Message File                                  */
     /*  Author  . . . : Thomas Raddatz   <thomas.raddatz@tools400.de>      */
